  "notes": "Twelve permanent backpack/suit upgrades — four categories (inventory, battery, oxygen, hydrogen) × three tiers (Mk 1/2/3). All use subcategory 'upgrade' (mod-extended enum — see schemas/resource-item.schema.json). Each record carries a single capacity multiplier in `effects`; multipliers REPLACE the previous tier (not additive) — equipping Mk 3 applies 3.0×, not 3.0 × 2.0 × 1.5. Tier chaining mirrors vanilla Drill Mk 1/2/3: Mk 2 consumes 1× Mk 1, Mk 3 consumes 1× Mk 2. Mass is constant within a family (15/12/10/12 kg for inventory/battery/oxygen/hydrogen). Crafting time ramps 4/6/8s. Vanilla reference capacities the multipliers scale: Power Cell 180 000 electricity units; Oxygen Tank 1.5m 8 000 units; Hydrogen Tank 1.5m 8 000 units. IMPORTANT: the Hydrogen Upgrade scales the baseline suit H₂ tank — it does NOT scale the jetpack_fuel_tank consumable's one-shot refill amount.",
